425: ## R24 — Approval modes en `requests.types.approval_chain_template` JSONB
426: 
427: Estructura definitiva:
428: 
429: ```json
430: {
431:   "mode": "parallel" | "direct_hr_admin" | "any_of_hr" | "parent_only",
432:   "visibility": "universal",
433:   "steps": [
434:     {
435:       "step_id": 1,
436:       "role": "supervisor" | "hr_admin" | "president",
437:       "resolver": "selected_supervisor_id" | "any_hr_admin" | "president_user",
