 29: 
 30: ## RLS strict (R2)
 31: 
 32: Toda tabla nueva en schemas HumanOS DEBE:
 33: 
 34: ```sql
 35: CREATE TABLE schema.tabla (...);
 36: 
 37: ALTER TABLE schema.tabla ENABLE ROW LEVEL SECURITY;
 38: 
 39: CREATE POLICY "policy_name" ON schema.tabla
 40:   FOR SELECT TO authenticated
 41:   USING (<condition>);
 42: -- + INSERT/UPDATE/DELETE policies según ownership
 43: ```
 44: 
 45: ---
 46: 
 47: ## Helper functions disponibles (NO redefinir)
 48: 
 49: | Function | Returns | Uso |
 50: |---|---|---|
 51: | `hr.current_person_id()` | uuid | person_id de auth.uid() actual |
 52: | `hr.current_app_role()` | text | employee \| hr_admin \| president \| admin (nuevo migration 025) |
 53: | `hr.is_hr_admin()` | boolean | true si app_role='hr_admin' |
 54: | `hr.is_president_or_admin()` | boolean | true si app_role IN ('president','admin') |
 55: | `hr.is_supervisor_of(person_id uuid)` | boolean | true si auth.uid() es supervisor_id de person_id |
 56: | `hr.has_direct_reports()` | boolean | true si auth.uid() tiene al menos un employment.supervisor_id apuntando a la persona (nuevo migration 025) |
 57: | `requests.can_view_ticket(ticket_id uuid)` | boolean | true si auth.uid() es requester, supervisor del requester, hr_admin, o president |
 58: 
