 60: 
 61: ## CHECK constraints críticos
 62: 
 63: | Tabla | Columna | CHECK |
 64: |---|---|---|
 65: | `hr.employments` | `app_role` | `IN ('employee', 'hr_admin', 'president', 'admin')` — 4 valores (sin 'supervisor') |
 66: | `hr.invite_codes` | `code` | `length(code) = 8` |
 67: | `hr.invite_codes` | `invite_method` | `IN ('email', 'whatsapp', 'paper', 'in_person')` |
 68: | `hr.user_settings` | `language` | `IN ('es', 'en')` |
 69: | `files.uploads` | `category` | `IS NULL OR IN ('attachment','evidence','signed_document','avatar','profile_photo','certificate_scan','payslip_proof','original_paper_form','medical_document','contract_document','incident_photo','identification_document','other')` |
