 74: ## SCD-2 pattern en `hr.employments` (R12)
 75: 
 76: ```sql
 77: -- Una sola is_current = TRUE por persona
 78: CREATE UNIQUE INDEX one_current_employment_per_person 
 79: ON hr.employments (person_id) WHERE is_current = TRUE;
 80: 
 81: -- Cambios críticos (position, supervisor, department, salary, app_role):
 82: -- 1. Cerrar viejo
 83: UPDATE hr.employments SET valid_to = CURRENT_DATE WHERE id = <id_actual>;
 84: 
 85: -- 2. Insertar nuevo (preserva history)
 86: INSERT INTO hr.employments (person_id, ..., valid_from, created_from, notes)
 87: VALUES (..., CURRENT_DATE, '<contexto_cambio>', '<razón_humana>');
 88: ```
 89: 
 90: `is_current` es generated column: `(valid_to IS NULL OR valid_to > CURRENT_DATE)`.
