 62: 
 63: - **B1 — Avatar upload step 10 RLS rejection**: nuevo server action `uploadOnboardingAvatarAction` en `src/lib/onboarding/actions.ts` (Task 12). Admin client gated por validez de invite_code (no consumed, no expirado) como auth proxy. Step 17.1 (`Step10PhotoConfirm.tsx`) llama el server action en lugar de `createSupabaseBrowserClient + uploadAvatar`. Helper `uploadAvatar` en `src/lib/storage/avatars.ts` preservado con comment indicando "use for F5 admin edit + F33 self-service, not wizard step 10". Path canonical `avatars/{person_id}/current.{ext}` consistente. β-prima preservado (pre-submit non-blocking + UX "continuar sin foto o reintentar").
